# Summary
Metrics in Amplitude are reusable analysis objects that can be created by any member, manager, or admin, but only managers and administrators can designate them as official. Available on Growth and Enterprise plans, metrics can be created as Event Segmentation, Revenue, Formula, or Funnel types, and are shared project-wide to accelerate workflows.

